<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bridge-vt">bridge <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /brɪdʒ/    美 /brɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>架桥于；把...连接起来；缩短...之间的距离：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A snack in the afternoon <strong>bridges the gap between</strong> lunch <strong>and</strong> supper.
在午餐和晚餐之间，下午吃些点心补充一下。</p></div></div>